These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: go, mah-jongg, backgammon, whist
City: rome, hamburg, new-york, liverpool
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, pakistani, russian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 2. the person playing go is in an even position##4
 3. the brazilian is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 7. the mexican is the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the person traveling to liverpool##2
10. the person playing go is the owner of the rat##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | backgammon  | go    | whist    | mah-jongg   |
| City   | hamburg     | rome   | new-york       | liverpool    |
| Nationality   | mexican | brazilian | russian    | pakistani |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

