.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, techno, dubstep, funk
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, poker, billiard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cycling, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 4. the fan of techno is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 7. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of dubstep is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing poker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre          | disco  | techno    | dubstep     | funk       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Game   | poker | mah-jongg   | scrabble   | billiard    |
| Sport         | cycling | volleyball  | biathlon | climbing   |

