There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
 2. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the dog is the italian##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the british##1
10. the owner of the dog is the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| City      | new-york | marseilles   | liverpool    | hannover      |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | woodworking | photography | traveling     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| Pet           | mouse         | dog       | hedgehog  | goat       |

