.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, oliveros, davidoff, old-henry
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, december, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the person drinking fanta is the prince-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the person drinking sprite is the old-henry-smoker##1
12. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | water       | sprite   | fanta   | iced-tea   |
| Cigar       | oliveros        | old-henry | prince    | davidoff       |
| Birthday      | july | march    | december  | november |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

