The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person traveling to new-york##2
 3. the manager is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the librarian is the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is the bartender##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is the librarian##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the librarian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
12. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
