The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, subway, trike
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person eating orange is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | iced-tea    | sprite  | juice      |
