 8. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the owner of the dog is between the person drinking tea and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
11. the person eating cranberry is in an even position##4
