 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
10. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar      | siglo   | pall-mall   | bolivar     | prince   |
| Nationality   | colombian  | thai       | australian | turkish |
| Movie-Genre           | fantasy     | thriller   | adventure     | epic     |
| Sport         | volleyball | ice-hockey | handball   | cycling |

