.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, tiparillo, dunhill, baccarat
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, van, boat, scooter
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
11. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
12. the ritmeester-smoker is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up        | milk        |
| Cigar         | baccarat | dunhill       | ritmeester | tiparillo |
| Transport   | scooter     | van        | roller    | boat      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

