.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, tulip, amaryllis
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bongani, dannemann, baccarat
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the fan of techno is the dannemann-smoker##1
 2. the dannemann-smoker is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 3. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the fan of house is the bongani-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is in an even position##4
 9. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
10. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
11. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Flower   | tulip | amaryllis  | daisy     | poppy |
| Cigar         | bongani    | blend | dannemann      | baccarat |
| Transport     | skateboard | car     | helicopter | bike       |

 